ces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最開心既日子係yr2同yr3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同教授好熟，得閒會出黎食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只想講雖<span style=\"color: red;\">然</span>人人際遇唔同，但你肯放開去識下人，讀大學可以好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"af0a367036b888e8fba95addf5a38953a260d108","tid":389322,"uid":86686,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:58:03.000Z","msg":"學識埋堆好、孤獨地努力都好<br />\n唔好一d（心態上/知識上)得著都冇就過左<br />\n唔好再用中學mindset喇，大學呢幾年真係好重要的。"},{"pid":"20ea31ea47fe8b68e72ad3c0867639a852b70be0","tid":389322,"uid":89166,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:04:25.000Z","msg":"就grad 都無歸屬感<br />\nyr1 個陣岩岩入大學 發現一間大學原來係咁多人<br />\n一科同屆都可以有咁多人<br />\n大學生活又有咁多組合<br />\n就知道根本無可能揾到所謂同路人<br />\n<br />\n中學個種一齊放學/放lunch 係大學係無乜可能見到<br />\n大家都係大家既過客 岩傾咪傾多一兩句<br />\n深交亦無需要 反正都係過客<br />\n<br />\n唯一問題係你要做 grp project 個陣會遇到實際問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef431037736e2bb932170ae2730a43cdcb49686","tid":389322,"uid":135901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:05:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔中意大學生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 讀一科自己唔中意嘅科好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsame 想quit 再rejupas由搵食科轉乞食科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想讀咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n哂銀時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"h