moji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想讀咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n哂銀時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家讀緊咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPoly其中一寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n晒銀時其實唔係你念咁有趣<br />\n特別係 phy/math 個啲 <br />\n<br />\n想讀咪問人攞 notes 讀下"},{"pid":"0dd45f4d7fa401cd01cd8f3e8d76a5e6b34ea441","tid":389322,"uid":35315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:24:09.000Z","msg":"大學只係職訓所（係社會逼成咁），記住依樣嘢就唔會對佢有咩期待，由我入個一刻我只係想靠佢個名同沙紙出黎搵食"},{"pid":"25c05dc0af2b977f504c8c8ca25f77d3530d596e","tid":389322,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:26:33.000Z","msg":"識左好多過客<br />\n有一年fd到仆街既fd<br />\n到final year冇住hall冇堂一齊已經收得皮"},{"pid":"460e943f90976f69b21805eab45d2996be026538","tid":389322,"uid":76514,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:34:37.000Z","msg":"以為自己夢遊開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日單機食飯 無hall無soc<br />\n我就嚟想走入廁所食飯"},{"pid":"31fa5fc89dae49378af66779e951b44d17ce55a6","tid":389322,"uid":141800,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:35:57.000Z","msg":"我識一個人，佢開場白係 Ching~~ 有冇梳屎呀<br />\n比完佢之後轉個頭已經唔記得我個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de6769e25f22fce0a55469a6137a14967a89d4d","tid":389322,"uid":70695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"